snippet.title: Frozen Fan Fest 2019 | Official Gameplay Teaser Trailer - 10/4/19
snippet.description:
Live at Frozen Fan Fest, you can preview our new match-3 puzzle and deco mobile game Disney Frozen Adventures! 

In Disney Frozen Adventures, you are the Royal Advisor and you decide how to decorate the Kingdom of Arendelle and beyond! 

With the help of Elsa, Anna, Olaf, Kristoff and Sven, you can solve all sorts of unique match-3 puzzles from collecting chocolate to uncovering trolls! Collect snowflakes from the match-3 puzzles to help you complete design tasks! There are hundreds of new challenges and quests that await you in Disney Frozen Adventures!

❄️❄️Pre-register for a FREE in-game gift! ❄️❄️

Subscribe to Frozen Adventures: https://jamcity.me/FA_PreReg_YT
Like our official Facebook page: https://www.facebook.com/frozenadventuresgame/
Follow us on Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/frozenadventuresgame/
Follow us on Twitter: https://twitter.com/frozenadvgame

Disney Frozen Adventures will be coming to Google Play and App Store in November 2019.
